# SLAM3R Study Repository — Licensing Overview

Last updated: 2025-09-20

This repository mixes original documentation authored by Warren Samuelson Jayakumar with source code that borrows/adapts from upstream research implementations. Different parts of the repository are licensed under different terms as outlined below.

